{"name": "Arc'teryx Gamma LT Pants - Men's", "categories": ["Home", "All", "Clothing", "Bottoms", "Pants", "Trousers", "Gamma LT Pants"], "description": "Climbing tomorrow, hiking next weekend, dream backpacking trip in a few months... playing outdoors can get complicated. Simplify things a bit with these versatile soft shell pants. Tough, lightweight and beautifully constructed, the Gamma LT pants have you covered for a wide range of activities. They're cut to accommodate dynamic movements, with articulated tailoring and plenty of stretch. The fit is close to the body with a straight leg, with a low profile brushed-back waistband that lies comfortably under a pack. Drawstring adjustable cuffs can be tightened to keep out bugs and trail debris, or hiked up out of the way for climbing.Face fabric is lightweight, durable and DWR-treated for water resistance.Soft, brushed polyester-lined waist has a snap closure and integrated adjustable webbing belt.Zip fly.2 mesh-lined hand pockets with laminated zip closure.Thigh pocket with laminated zip.Gusseted crotch, articulated knee and stretch for freedom of movement.Straight leg.Laminated cuffs with adjustable drawcord.Reflective logo.", "product_code": "6000-910", "tech_specs": {"Weight": ["350g (Medium)"], "Ideal for": ["Rock climbing", "Camping and hiking", "Alpine climbing and mountaineering"], "Type": ["Soft shell"], "Fabric content": ["88% nylon", "12% elastane"], "Waterproofness\n\nWaterproof garments use waterproof-breathable technologies and are fully seam-taped. Water-resistant garments use waterproof-breathable technologies but their seams are not taped. Water-resistant garments repel water and protect against wind but are not made of waterproof fabric.": ["Water-resistant"], "Pockets": ["1 thigh", "2 front zippered"], "Windproofness\n\nA windproof garment does not allow any air to permeate the fabric.  A garment with windproof panels has panels of fabric that are totally windproof, but the rest of the garment may